MIOS 0000000100000101 4,5,8,9,10 true MIOS is a required element in Gamecube gameplay. Without it, Gamecube games will not run. You can reinstall a good copy to restore Gamecube capabilities if this should occur.
BC 0000000100000100 2,4,5,6 true BC plays a role in Gamecube functions. Removal or corruption of BC will result in no Gamecube support. This can be fixed with the installation of a proper BC.
